{title: Ole Slew Foot}
{artist: Johnny Horton}
{composer: unknown}

[G]High on the mountain tell me what you see
Bear tracks bear tracks [C]looking back at [G]me
Better get your rifle boys before it's too late
'Cause a bear's got a little pig and [C]headed thru the [G]gate
He's [D7]big around the middle and he's [G]broad across the rump
Running [D7]ninety miles an hour taking [G]thirty feet a jump
Ain't never been caught he ain't never been tree'd
